OL,3,CEngland kicks off against Norway as
OL,4,Cboth seek spot in World Cup semi-finals
OL,6,FEngland has kicked off their game
OL,7,Fagainst Norway as both sides seek a
OL,8,Fspot in the World Cup semi-finals.
OL,10,FThe Three Lions are hoping to contain
OL,11,Ftheir star player, Erling Haaland,
OL,12,Fwhile relying on Harry Kane and Jude
OL,13,FBellingham to put them ahead.
OL,15,FJohn Stones and Noni Madueke came into
OL,16,Fthe England team as Thomas Tuchel made
OL,17,Ftwo changes for the game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
