OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783873241
OL,3,CEngland kicks off against Norway as
OL,4,Cboth seek spot in World Cup semi-finals
OL,6,FStones, who recently left Manchester
OL,7,FCity as a free agent, will play
OL,8,Fcentral defence alongside Marc Guehi,
OL,9,Fwho has shaken off a hamstring injury,
OL,10,Fwith the duo putting club allegiances
OL,11,Fto one side as they try to keep City's
OL,12,FErling Haaland quiet.
OL,14,FEzri Konsa has shifted over to right-
OL,15,Fback as he did in the last-16 win
OL,16,Fagainst Mexico following the red card
OL,17,Fto Jarell Quansah, who begins a two-
OL,18,Fmatch ban.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
