PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1783873241
OL,3,CEngland kicks off against Norway as
OL,4,Cboth seek spot in World Cup semi-finals
OL,6,FMadueke returns to the team in place
OL,7,Fof Arsenal team-mate Bukayo Saka, who
OL,8,Fis still managing an Achilles injury.
OL,10,FKane has scored six goals, equalling
OL,11,Fhis tally from the 2018 World Cup,
OL,12,Fwhile Haaland's seven have fired
OL,13,FNorway to their first quarter-final.
OL,15,FBayern Munich's Kane is enjoying a
OL,16,Frecord-breaking season, scoring 73
OL,17,Fgoals for club and country, including
OL,18,Fsix in the World Cup, while Manchester
OL,19,FCity star Haaland has bagged 58, with
OL,20,Fhis seven at the tournament firing
OL,21,FNorway to a first-ever quarter-final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
