OL,3,CEngland kicks off against Norway as
OL,4,Cboth seek spot in World Cup semi-finals
OL,6,FAs expected, Haaland leads Norway's
OL,7,Fline with several recognisable names
OL,8,Ffrom English clubs, including
OL,9,FArsenal's Martin Odegaard, Brentford
OL,10,Fdefender Kristoffer Ajer and Fulham's
OL,11,FSander Berge.
OL,13,FGoalkeeper Jordan Pickford has made
OL,14,Fhis record 18th World Cup appearance,
OL,15,Fputting him in front of England great
OL,16,FPeter Shilton.
OL,18,FTemperatures are soaring at 33C, but
OL,19,Fthe Florida humidity makes it feel
OL,20,Flike 44C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
