OL,3,CEngland kicks off against Norway as
OL,4,Cboth seek spot in World Cup semi-finals
OL,6,FThis hasn't stopped England fans
OL,7,Fturning out in droves for the game,
OL,8,Fwith many turning up hours before kick-
OL,9,Foff to get their seats for the match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
